    prop:change_at base:day_seven ;
    prop:extractedFrom "Subgroup analysis revealed a similar occurrence of mortality in immunoparalysis-associated multi-organ failure (IPMOF) (16/26 vs. 14/21); 95% CI, p (0.60-1.42, p=0.71) at 28 days, and 2 median dose of filgrastim (G-CSF) for 3 median day did not significantly change the TNF-α levels within the intervention group at day seven (56 [32-118] vs. 19 [6.9-118], p=0.77) as compared to day 0." ;
