    rdfs:label "DeLong" ;
    prop:confirm base:sepsis ;
    prop:extractedFrom """Statistical comparison using DeLong’s test confirmed that the AUC of ePWV was significantly higher than that of both SIRS (P < 0.001) and SOFA (P = 0.002). The non-overlapping 95%CI further support the robustness of these differences. 
Fig. 2Assessment of association between ePWV and in-hospital mortality risk in sepsis patients
 Assessment of association between ePWV and in-hospital mortality risk in sepsis patients 
Fig. 3A.""" ;
