    prop:adopt_Unlike base:Wang_C_Y ;
    prop:extractedFrom "Unlike the first version of GMMAD (Wang C. Y. et al., 2023), which was based on qualitative annotations (e.g., labeling microbes as beneficial or harmful in specific diseases), GMMAD v2.0 adopts a quantitative framework that integrates gut micro biome abundance data to evaluate metabolite-level alterations more precisely across disease states." ;
