base:Impella a type:Product ;
    rdfs:label "Impella" ;
    prop:extractedFrom "Impella provides a continuous antegrade circulatory flow of 3.7–5.5 l/min for a maximum duration of 14 days [6], though numerous reports of Impella 5.5 implementation for up to 70 days are available [7].",
        "The choice of MCS (Impella vs. VA-ECMO) depends on patient characteristics: Impella is preferred for isolated left ventricular dysfunction, while VA-ECMO is used for biventricular failure (42)." ;
