    prop:extractedFrom "Briefly, patients who received cefepime in the PICU during the study collection periods had residual blood in ethylenediaminetetraacetic acid (EDTA) or lithium-heparin tubes requested from the clinical laboratory.",
        "Patients without baseline dialysis dependence but who received dialysis in the PICU had creatinine values (and therefore eGFR estimates) analysed only for days before initiation of renal replacement therapies." ;
    prop:have base:days,
        base:heparin ;
