base:il_6 a type:Biomarker ;
    rdfs:label "il-6" ;
    prop:achieve_In base:sepsis ;
    prop:associate_with base:sepsis ;
    prop:correlate_with base:ISS ;
    prop:demonstrate_In base:sepsis ;
    prop:differentiate_from base:Fang ;
    prop:extractedFrom "A combination of CRP, PCT, and IL-6 improves diagnostic precision for systemic inflammation, while PCT, IL-8, and IL-10 are useful for the early detection of organ dysfunction[57].",
        "Although early serum levels of PCT, hs-CRP, and IL-6 were associated with the severity of burn sepsis, their prognostic value for predicting outcomes was relatively low.",
        "Body temperature, WBC, and IL-6 have limited diagnostic value.",
        "However, some studies still show that IL-6 cannot predict mortality in non-burn sepsis patients.68,69",
        "IL-6 correlated significantly with ISS at all time points.",
        "In a study, combinations of IL-8 and IL-6, MCP-1 and HSP70, and hyaluronan and IL-6 achieved perfect discrimination between sepsis patients and healthy controls (AUC of 1.00), underscoring the potential of multi-biomarker panels in enhancing diagnostic accuracy[5].",
        "In contrast, body temperature, WBC, and IL-6 levels demonstrated limited utility for early diagnosis of burn sepsis.",
        "Serum HBP and IL-6 have comparable predictive efficacy to SOFA score and are numerically superior to PCT, CRP, and Lac.",
        "Serum levels of TLR2, TLR4, TLR9, IL-1β, IL-6, IL-8, IL-10, TNF-α and IFN-γ were quantified by enzyme-linked immunosorbent assay at the time of sepsis diagnosis.",
        "The distinctive triad of significant lymphocytopenia, hyperinflammation (evidenced by elevated levels of CRP, PCT, and IL-6), and hypoalbuminemia differentiates it from typical CAP, where such pronounced immune dysregulation is less prevalent (Fang et al., 2025; Yang et al., 2022).",
        "They found that a combination of elevated IL-6 and IL-12 p70 and lower TNF had an elevated risk of dying of sepsis." ;
    prop:have base:pct,
        base:sepsis,
        base:sofa_score ;
    prop:improve base:pct ;
